OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,7,FCarter
OL,9,FUS President Donald Trump has accused
OL,10,Fthe UK of "great stupidity" over its
OL,11,Fdecision to return sovereignty of the
OL,12,FChagos Islands to Mauritius.
OL,14,FThe president had, until recently,
OL,15,Fappeared on board with the deal, which
OL,16,Fincludes a formal transfer of Diego
OL,17,FGarcia, home to a key US military base.
