OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FHis objection to the agreement is the
OL,7,Flatest development in what has been a
OL,8,Frocky passage for Sir Keir Starmer,
OL,9,Fand now the most recent stumbling
OL,10,Fblock to the government's agenda.
OL,12,FBut what is the deal, and why is it so
OL,13,Fcontroversial? ITV News explains.
OL,15,FWhat are the Chagos Islands?
OL,17,FThe Chagos Islands are an archipelago
OL,18,Fin the Indian Ocean, approximately
OL,19,F1,250 miles north-east of Mauritius.
