OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FThe largest of the islands, Diego
OL,7,FGarcia, is home to a joint UK-US
OL,8,Fmilitary base.
OL,10,FIn 1814, the islands became classed as
OL,11,Fa British territory, while still being
OL,12,Fgoverned by Mauritius.
