OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FThe remote chain of more than 60
OL,7,Fislands is located in the middle of
OL,8,Fthe Indian Ocean off the tip of India,
OL,9,Fsouth of the Maldives. But they are
OL,10,Fhugely strategically important.
OL,12,FThe UK-US military base on Diego
OL,13,FGarcia has supported US military
OL,14,Foperations from Vietnam to Iraq and
OL,15,FAfghanistan. In 2008, the US
OL,16,Facknowledged it also had been used for
OL,17,Fclandestine rendition flights of
OL,18,Fterror suspects.
