OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FMore recently, the US deployed several
OL,7,Fnuclear-capable B-2 Spirit bombers to
OL,8,FDiego Garcia amid an intense airstrike
OL,9,Fcampaign targeting Yemen's Houthi
OL,10,Frebels.
OL,12,FThe US has described the base, which
OL,13,Fis home to about 2,500 mostly American
OL,14,Fpersonnel, as an "all but
OL,15,Findispensable platform" for security
OL,16,Foperations in the Middle East, South
OL,17,FAsia and East Africa.
OL,19,FWhy is the UK returning them to
OL,20,FMauritius?
