OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FIn the 1980s, Mauritius claimed
OL,7,Fsovereignty over the islands.
OL,9,FIn 2019, the International Court of
OL,10,FJustice (ICJ) ruled in its favour,
OL,11,Fsaying the UK was "under an obligation
OL,12,Fto bring to an end its administration
OL,13,Fof the archipelago as rapidly as
OL,14,Fpossible".
OL,16,FThe Conservative government, under
OL,17,FRishi Sunak, began the negotiations to
OL,18,Freturn the Chagos Islands, and
OL,19,FStarmer's Labour government finalised
OL,20,Fthe deal, announcing it in May 2025.
