OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FStarmer said the deal was necessary,
OL,7,Fbecause the UK would "not have a
OL,8,Frealistic prospect of success" of
OL,9,Fwinning a legal fight against
OL,10,FMauritius, given the ICJ's ruling.
OL,12,FFailure to secure a deal threatened
OL,13,Fthe legitimacy of the Diego Garcia
OL,14,Fbase and ran the risk of hostile
OL,15,Fstates like China establishing
OL,16,Fmilitary bases on neighbouring islands.
OL,18,FUnder the agreed deal, a 24-nautical-
OL,19,Fmile buffer zone would be put in place
OL,20,Faround the island where nothing can be
OL,21,Fbuilt or placed without UK consent.
