OL,6,FWhat terms were agreed in the deal?
OL,8,FOn October 3, the UK announced a deal
OL,9,Fwhich would see the sovereignty of the
OL,10,Fremote Chagos Islands handed to
OL,11,FMauritius.
OL,13,FThat deal also includes Diego Garcia.
OL,15,FUnder the terms of the deal, the UK
OL,16,Fwould cede sovereignty of the islands
OL,17,Fto Mauritius, making it the first time
OL,18,Fin 50 years that the status of the
OL,19,Fislands would be undisputed and
OL,20,Flegally secure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
