OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FCritics of proposals to hand over the
OL,7,Fislands to Mauritius fear the move
OL,8,Fwill benefit China, which has a
OL,9,Fgrowing reach in the region.
OL,11,FThe Conservatives claimed Sir Keir
OL,12,FStarmer had offended the Chagossian
OL,13,Fpeople when he said opponents of his
OL,14,Fdeal to hand over the Chagos Islands
OL,15,Fwere akin to Russia, China and Iran.
