OL,6,FShadow Foreign Secretary Dame Priti
OL,7,FPatel said: "Starmer has slandered the
OL,8,FChagossian community, and he is so
OL,9,Farrogant and out of touch with British
OL,10,Fvalues and the national interest that
OL,11,Fhe has resorted to baseless and
OL,12,Fdisgusting slurs ` whilst he himself
OL,13,Fhands control of Chagos to a country
OL,14,Fthat is actually cosying up with
OL,15,FRussia and China.
OL,17,F"Today is a day of shame for our
OL,18,Fcountry and Keir Starmer and David
OL,19,FLammy are the chief architects of it."
