OL,6,FThe deal was also subject to a last-
OL,7,Fminute legal hurdle, when hours before
OL,8,Fit was due to be signed, a legal
OL,9,Fchallenge prevented its completion,
OL,10,Fwith Mr Justice Goose granting an
OL,11,Finjunction against the FCDO for
OL,12,F"interim relief".
OL,14,FThe legal challenge had been brought
OL,15,Fagainst the Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,16,FDevelopment Office (FCDO) by two
OL,17,FBritish women born on the Chagos
OL,18,FIslands, but was dismissed in the High
OL,19,FCourt.
