OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FTrump initially seemed to oppose the
OL,7,Fdeal, with his close ally Nigel Farage
OL,8,Ffrequently referencing this in
OL,9,FCommons' debates.
OL,11,FDespite this, Trump signed the
OL,12,Fagreement last year, with US Secretary
OL,13,Fof State Marco Rubio saying it
OL,14,F"secures the long-term, stable and
OL,15,Feffective operation of the joint US-UK
OL,16,Fmilitary facility at Diego Garcia,
OL,17,Fwhich is critical to regional and
OL,18,Fglobal security".
