OL,3,CWhat is the UK Chagos Island deal and
OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FThe deal looks to be in jeopardy
OL,7,Fagain, however, after Trump took to
OL,8,Fhis social media platform Truth Social
OL,9,Fin the early hours of Tuesday morning
OL,10,Fto attack the agreement, linking it to
OL,11,Fhis ambitions to acquire Greenland.
OL,13,FIn a direct attack on the UK, the
OL,14,Fpresident called the Chagos decision
OL,15,F"another in a very long line of
OL,16,FNational Security reasons why
OL,17,FGreenland has to be acquired".
