OL,4,Cwhy does Trump think it is 'stupid'?
OL,6,FHis comments come a day after Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer attempted to de-escalate
OL,8,Ftensions between Washington and
OL,9,FEurope, telling an emergency address
OL,10,Fhe thought the situation could "be
OL,11,Fresolved and should be resolved
OL,12,Fthrough calm discussion".
OL,14,FOn his social media platform, Trump
OL,15,Fwrote on Tuesday: "Shockingly, our
OL,16,F'brilliant' NATO Ally, the United
OL,17,FKingdom, is currently planning to give
OL,18,Faway the Island of Diego Garcia, the
OL,19,Fsite of a vital US Military Base, to
OL,20,FMauritius, and to do so FOR NO REASON
OL,21,FWHATSOEVER.
